Vaswani Industries Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 30/05/2025 inter alia to consider and approve meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled to be held on Friday 30th May 2025 inter alia to.

1) Consider and approve the Standalone Financial Results of the Company for the quarter and financial year ended 31st March 2025;
2) Consider and approve the Standalone Financial Statements of the Company for the financial year ended 31st March 2025
